data.description: This beautiful 4 bedroom 2 1/2 bath home is located in a quiet cul-de-sac with a wonderful, landscaped yard that is Fully fenced. The entrance foyer opens to a formal dining room and a large great room with a gas log fireplace and built-in cabinets and shelves. The kitchen is very large for this 2555 square foot house, and it has dining area with built-in cabinets and a separate desk area. The kitchen has a large bar counter with a separate island and all the countertops are siltstone. The laundry room is a nice size for all needs and more. The half bath is located off the back door that leads to the carport. The kitchen, great room and main bedroom have doors leading to a glass/screened in porch that overlooks a beautiful patio and large backyard. The 3 other bedrooms share a hall bathroom, and they have good closet space. The main bedroom has a trey ceiling and a "Texas walk-through" main bath. His and her sinks and his and her closets with a separate shower and jetted tub. If you need storage... this house has two storage rooms off the carport and floored attic space. This house is a wonderful move in ready home. New roof was put on in 2019.
